  "remarks": "Grinex is a crypto-currency exchange registered in Kyrgyzstan. Grinex is a major platform for trading the stablecoin A7A5, which is collateralised by PSB Bank, a Russian State-owned institution. For every rouble spent on A7A5, an equivalent sum is deposited into PSB Bank, thereby increasing the State-owned institution’s capital. A7A5 was developed by LLC A7 and PSB Bank, and is issued by LLC Old Vector.",
